516
01:03:29,873 --> 01:03:31,633
Good.

517
01:03:39,353 --> 01:03:42,193
No, no, no. I already got it.

518
01:03:44,113 --> 01:03:46,433
No, no, no. Over here.

519
01:04:01,871 --> 01:04:05,678
This was Sonja's favorite bakery.

520
01:04:07,511 --> 01:04:12,909
Every Thursday at 1:00 we sat here.
