old grudges behind us.

555
01:07:17,036 --> 01:07:22,036
- We just had to talk again.
- I've been thinking.

556
01:07:22,989 --> 01:07:27,429
Isn't it time we put old grudges behind us?

557
01:07:33,589 --> 01:07:36,069
