His Dad doesn't know about it.

617
01:13:25,575 --> 01:13:30,989
I don't go around talking
about what others do.

618
01:13:32,483 --> 01:13:35,923
- You have a much worse problem.
- What's that?

619
01:13:36,083 --> 01:13:38,883
